en-houthis-ships-attacked/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装加大对红海船只的攻击力度，但国际社会对此反应甚少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-ships-in-red-sea-with-little-international-response/0000018c-6d6a-de43-affd-fd6ad2b60000</link><description>周四，两艘外国商船在红海和阿拉伯海遭到袭击。据报道，周五，胡塞武装继续向国际海上贸易施压，另一艘船在该地区遭到袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-ships-in-red-sea-with-little-international-response/0000018c-6d6a-de43-affd-fd6ad2b60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布三名士兵在加沙战斗中死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-deaths-of-three-soldiers-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-6ddb-d798-adac-edff75360000</link><description>三名死去的以色列士兵是中士。谢伊·尤里尔·皮泽姆 (Shay Uriel Pizem) 少校，23 岁，中士。奥兹·什穆埃尔·阿拉迪 (Oz Shmuel Aradi)，19 岁，军士长。托梅尔·什洛莫·迈亚拉，28 岁</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-deaths-of-three-soldiers-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-6ddb-d798-adac-edff75360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察在东耶路撒冷拍摄到袭击阿拉伯记者的画面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officers-filmed-attacking-arab-journalist-in-east-jerusalem/0000018c-6da2-dbd5-a39c-fff36db10000</link><description>摄影记者穆斯塔法·哈鲁夫 (Mustafa Al-Haruf) 在东耶路撒冷瓦迪乔兹 (Wadi Joz) 社区记录周五的祈祷时遭到边防警察的袭击。两名涉事警员被停职，事件正在调查中</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officers-filmed-attacking-arab-journalist-in-east-jerusalem/0000018c-6da2-dbd5-a39c-fff36db10000</guid></item><item><title>对美国武器的依赖迫使内塔尼亚胡接受拜登的战争要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/reliance-on-u-s-weapons-forces-netanyahu-to-accept-bidens-war-requests/0000018c-6d45-dbd5-a39c-ff7706f50000</link><description>这位美国总统正试图平衡他对以色列的支持和来自他的支持者的压力，以制定以色列的战时政策。事实证明，军事援助计划是美国对以色列的最佳筹码</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 13:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/reliance-on-u-s-weapons-forces-netanyahu-to-accept-bidens-war-requests/0000018c-6d45-dbd5-a39c-ff7706f50000</guid></item><item><title>“几乎完全有罪不罚的环境”：英国带头呼吁以色列解决定居者暴力问题 15 个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/britain-leads-15-nation-call-on-israel-to-tackle-west-bank-settler-violence/0000018c-6d31-d798-adac-edbf772b0000</link><description>法国、加拿大、澳大利亚等十几个国家强调，“以色列作为占领国，必须采取积极措施保护约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦平民”。西方政府正在制定旅行禁令的标准，并正在收集相关名称</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/britain-leads-15-nation-call-on-israel-to-tackle-west-bank-settler-violence/0000018c-6d31-d798-adac-edbf772b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列国防军从加沙救出三具被哈马斯杀害的以色列人质尸体，其中包括两名士兵</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/idf-rescues-three-bodies-of-hamas-slain-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-including-two-soldiers/0000018c-6cb4-de43-affd-fcb6e9450000</link><description>尼克·贝瑟、罗恩·谢尔曼和埃利亚·托莱达诺的尸体于周五被打捞并运回以色列；以色列国防军没有提供有关三名人质死亡情况的信息</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 10:03:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/idf-rescues-three-bodies-of-hamas-slain-israeli-hostages-from-gaza-including-two-soldiers/0000018c-6cb4-de43-affd-fcb6e9450000</guid></item><item><title>该营唯一的女性是拯救受伤士兵生命的医生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/battalions-only-woman-is-doctor-who-saves-wounded-troops-lives/0000018c-69f2-d798-adac-edff42660000</link><description>27 岁的丹妮拉·阿加耶夫 (Daniella Agaev) 博士对她所在的营至关重要，她并不关心自己是团队中唯一的女性。自十月地面行动开始以来，她几乎没有离开过加沙，并拯救了许多战友的生命</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 04:00:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/battalions-only-woman-is-doctor-who-saves-wounded-troops-lives/0000018c-69f2-d798-adac-edff42660000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡顽固拒绝讨论“后天”也危及以色列军队在加沙的成就</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refusal-to-discuss-the-day-after-endangers-the-idfs-achievements-in-gaza/0000018c-69d3-de43-affd-fdd31add0000</link><description>最近几天，地面进攻的沉重代价已经变得显而易见，而且可能会造成更多受害者 ■ 以色列很快将不得不解决埃及的担忧，并且还将发现美国的支持是有条件的</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 04:00:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/netanyahus-refusal-to-discuss-the-day-after-endangers-the-idfs-achievements-in-gaza/0000018c-69d3-de43-affd-fdd31add0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙火箭弹袭击耶路撒冷；航运巨头马士基暂停红海业务</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-live/senior-u-s-official-hamas-leader-sinwars-days-are-numbered/0000018c-6b87-db38-a9fc-eba7b5250000</link><description>以色列国防军从加沙救出三名人质，其中包括两名以色列国防军士兵 ■ 加沙火箭弹袭击耶路撒冷及其周边地区 ■ 美国国家安全顾问表示，战争将持续数月，将在以色列访问期间分阶段针对哈马斯领导层 ■ 商船被击中也门附近的枪击事件 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙仍有超过 138 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙有 18,608 人死亡、50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 03:42:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-live/senior-u-s-official-hamas-leader-sinwars-days-are-numbered/0000018c-6b87-db38-a9fc-eba7b5250000</guid></item><item><title>极右翼部长签署以色列国防军允许约旦河西岸巴勒斯坦人在以色列定居点工作的决定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-okayed-decision-to-allow-west-bank-palestinians-to-work-in-settlements/0000018c-6a3b-db38-a9fc-ebbb9ccb0000</link><description>以色列国防军允许 10,000 名巴勒斯坦人在这些领土上的定居点和工厂工作，但他们仍被禁止进入以色列。一位国防消息人士称，“这纯粹是虚伪的：定居者酋长和部长反对他们进入以色列，但却是第一个要求他们在定居点工作的人”</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 01:03:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/far-right-ministers-okayed-decision-to-allow-west-bank-palestinians-to-work-in-settlements/0000018c-6a3b-db38-a9fc-ebbb9ccb0000</guid></item><item><title>“当人们热爱以色列并想住在这里时，即使他们不是犹太人，你能做什么？”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-15/ty-article/.highlight/what-can-you-do-when-people-love-israel-and-want-to-live-here-even-if-theyre-not-jews/0000018c-6a9f-d798-adac-eebf41b40000</link><description>本周在本古里安机场：一对以色列-摩尔多瓦夫妇因官僚主义而四分五裂，一位以色列食品专家通过采集和发酵工作坊帮助失去亲人的家庭应对悲伤</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 23:41:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/holylandings/2023-12-15/ty-article/.highlight/what-can-you-do-when-people-love-israel-and-want-to-live-here-even-if-theyre-not-jews/0000018c-6a9f-d798-adac-eebf41b40000</guid></item><item><title>“辛瓦尔告诉我：有一天我会掌权，而你将成为接受审讯的人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/sinwar-told-me-one-day-ill-be-in-power-and-youll-be-the-one-interrogated/0000018c-6a50-db38-a9fc-ebf2e85f0000</link><description>20 世纪 80 年代，负责审问叶海亚·辛瓦尔 (Yahya Sinwar) 的辛贝特审讯员讲述了他与哈马斯领导人的惊心动魄的遭遇。官员预测辛瓦尔将支持巴勒斯坦囚犯人质交换——但不会被以色列俘虏</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 23:15:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/sinwar-told-me-one-day-ill-be-in-power-and-youll-be-the-one-interrogated/0000018c-6a50-db38-a9fc-ebf2e85f0000</guid></item><item><title>塞法迪首席拉比谴责以色列士兵不尊重清真寺的图像</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/sephardic-chief-rabbi-decries-images-of-israeli-soldiers-disrespecting-mosques/0000018c-69bf-db38-a9fc-e9bf58740000</link><description>拉比伊扎克·约瑟夫（Yitzhak Yosef）写信给以色列国防军首席拉比，称士兵亵渎圣地的图像“对以色列人民及其在世界上的形象造成损害”，并表示应该向士兵解释“成员的感受”其他宗教的信仰不应受到伤害”</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 21:03:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/.premium/sephardic-chief-rabbi-decries-images-of-israeli-soldiers-disrespecting-mosques/0000018c-69bf-db38-a9fc-e9bf58740000</guid></item><item><title>以色列退伍军人在特别选举中被任命为共和党候选人，取代乔治·桑托斯</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-military-veteran-tapped-as-gop-candidate-in-special-election-to-replace-george-santos/0000018c-69f8-db38-a9fc-e9fafd2c0000</link><description>拿骚县议员、前以色列伞兵马兹·皮利普(Mazi Pilip)将在桑托斯空出的席位的特别选举中与民主党前国会议员汤姆·索兹(Tom Suozzi)对决</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 20:16:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-12-14/ty-article/israeli-military-veteran-tapped-as-gop-candidate-in-special-election-to-replace-george-santos/0000018c-69f8-db38-a9fc-e9fafd2c0000</guid></item><item><title>不仅仅是否认暴行和悲凉：为什么这次巴勒斯坦民意调查很重要</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-14/ty-article/.highlight/not-only-atrocity-denial-and-desolation-why-this-palestinian-poll-matters/0000018c-696a-d798-adac-edef198b0000</link><description>在 10 月 7 日之前，巴勒斯坦政策和调查研究中心的这些发现将被认为对两国解决方案不利。现在他们应该给予安慰</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 19:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2023-12-14/ty-article/.highlight/not-only-atrocity-denial-and-desolation-why-this-palestinian-poll-matters/0000018c-696a-d798-adac-edef198b0000</guid></item><item><title>欧洲各地因恐怖阴谋联合调查逮捕七人，嫌疑人与哈马斯有关</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-14/ty-article/seven-individuals-arrested-across-europe-over-terror-plot-suspects-linked-to-hamas/0000018c-6948-d798-adac-edefd7dd0000</link><description>摩萨德周四在一份声明中表示，丹麦因“代表”哈马斯针对平民的恐怖阴谋而逮捕了七人。目前尚不清楚这七次逮捕是否指的是在欧洲进行的所有逮捕，或者是否还有丹麦当局未报告的其他逮捕事件</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 19:11:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-12-14/ty-article/seven-individuals-arrested-across-europe-over-terror-plot-suspects-linked-to-hamas/0000018c-6948-d798-adac-edefd7dd0000</guid></item><item><title>随着中国站在巴勒斯坦一边，加沙战争可能会加强以色列与台湾的关系</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-china-sides-with-palestinians-gaza-war-could-strengthen-israeli-ties-with-taiwan/0000018c-6842-dbd5-a39c-ff7356050000</link><description>中国媒体告诉世界，美国因欧洲和加沙战争而分心，可能会在一月份选举前危及台湾。然而，中国回应的一个副作用可能是促使以色列和台湾走得更近</description><pubDate>Thu, 14 Dec 2023 18:35:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-14/ty-article-magazine/.premium/as-china-sides-with-palestinians-gaza-war-could-strengthen-israeli-ties-with-taiwan/0000018c-6842-dbd5-a39c-ff7356050000</guid></item></channel></rss>